| `shadow-md` | `0 2px 8px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.06)` | Cards (optional — prefer border-only cards) |
| `shadow-lg` | `0 8px 24px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.10)` | Modals, dropdowns, popovers |
| `shadow-none` | `none` | Default — most elements have no shadow |

