  FOR SELECT USING (user_id = (SELECT auth.uid()));
```

**INSERT**
```sql
CREATE POLICY "notifications_insert" ON notifications
  FOR INSERT
  WITH CHECK ((SELECT auth.uid()) IS NOT NULL);
  -- Any authenticated user can trigger a notification (for another user).
```

**UPDATE**
```sql
